Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Assigned' occurring in variants that eventually lead to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Percentage of variants containing 'Accepted + Assigned' that do not include 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all cases where 'Completed + In Call' does not happen

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + Assigned' is directly followed by 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities that occur after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Assigned' in high-performance variants (performance < 500,000 time units)
Metric: the average of the function base < 500000 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' relative to the frequency of 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Number of variants where 'Accepted + Assigned' appears more than once
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities

Name: Percentage of cases containing 'Accepted + Assigned' that end in 'Completed + Closed' versus those ending in 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants that include any 'Accepted + Wait' subtype activity
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' occurrences that are part of loops involving 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Ratio of 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Number of times 'Accepted + Assigned' precedes a wait state (e.g., 'Accepted + Wait - User', 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor', or 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation')
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities that occur in cases with total duration above the median case duration
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants originating directly from 'Accepted + In Progress' without intermediate queuing
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Percentage of all 'Accepted + Assigned' instances that are followed within three steps by 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Number of distinct cases in which 'Accepted + Assigned' appears at least once
Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities

Name: Percentage of variants containing 'Accepted + Assigned' that also contain more than one occurrence of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Assigned' compared to the combined frequency of all 'Accepted + Wait' subtypes
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' activities that occur in the first half of their respective case lifecycles
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Assigned' out of all cases
